narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Team Nurse, Inc. is a Durable Medical Equipment & Medical Supplies provider based in South Boston, VA. From 2018-08 through 2019-06, this provider received $56K in Medicaid payments across 878 claims serving 180 beneficiaries, billing 2 distinct procedure codes.

narrative.title: Key Findings
items: 91% of all billing comes from a single procedure code: T1019 (T1019). This extreme concentration is unusual and may indicate specialized services or a narrow billing pattern.
Billing stopped in 2019-06, suggesting this provider is no longer active in Medicaid. Abrupt cessation of billing can be a risk indicator.
